{"tid":1679162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行動唔升級 香港一定輸","createTime":"2019-10-28T04:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T08:15:43.000Z","uid":109262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e354167c7ba9a07435f53018dd62b1fd4f481e27","tid":1679162,"uid":109262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:51:22.000Z","msg":"警: 尋晚旺角冇差別拘捕<br />\n政府: 陳帆&quot;社會對港鐵無攻擊意念 服務才會恢復正常&quot;<br />\n777: 繼續不回應<br />\n<br />\n運動已經膠着狀態, <br />\n你睇吓IG幾多人去海洋公園玩?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好快又到聖誕, 和理性一定會掛住玩<br />\n<br />\n重唔把握時間?!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">裝修要繼續，黨鐵要收皮!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SKUEhcR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSKUEhcR.jpg&h=e78ae179&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09983b6c68df44b3242a6adeef7a601d6936e848","tid":1679162,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:51:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"00df5bcad7a01fef1c80cb5e47d454628f136019","tid":1679162,"uid":109262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:02:10.000Z","msg":"驕兵必敗<br />\n唔好睇少聖誕, 對和理非嘅威力<br />\n<br />\n人一少咗, 勇武巴打冇晒掩護<br />\n國際戰線會冇晒聲氣<br />\n<br />\n贏係贏緊，但係一定要行動升級<br />\n<br />\n以港豬鍾意飲囍茶+食海底撈嘅性格<br />\n求其鳩假期唱一唱啲藍店,<br />\n黃色經濟圈就會崩潰"},{"pid":"18266b4d9365606e2a6d901bcbce9f0bf294de41","tid":1679162,"uid":109262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:03:58.000Z","msg":"我唔知做乜,<br />\n對家一味風向我哋輸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係你開IG睇吓幾多人去海洋公園玩?<br />\nfeel到危機感未??<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n同意嘅幫手推post</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"435ebf3eefd